'''Kuwada Shrine''' in Umahori is the second candidate shrine. Its former rank was mukakusha.

=== Enshrined deity ===
* {{ill|lt=Ichikishimahime|Q11059454|qid=Q11059454|qid=Q11059454|lt=Ichikishimahime-no-Mikoto|1=Ichikishima-hime}}

=== History ===
Its history is unclear. A tradition says the deity was moved from this site to the Yamamoto site.<ref name=chosa/>

